        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Mike Taylor was appointed as a non executive board member on 1 March 2013. He was re-appointed for a second term 1 March 2014 and a third term on the 1 March 2017.  He founded Innovise Ltd in 2003 and as chief executive officer has led the companyâ€™s rapid buy-and-build growth.</p>

<p>Mike began his professional career as a research analyst in the City of London. He rose to director level and headed the media research team at Credit Suisse First Boston. He was involved in a number of high profile capital raising exercises there before leaving the City of London in 2003.</p>
</div>
      </section>

